"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Visual Timeline"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Exchange 1: User asks question\n  ↓\n  +500 tokens (user input)\n  ↓\n  +800 tokens (Claude response)\n  ↓\n  Total: 1,300 tokens\n\nExchange 2: User responds\n  ↓\n  +400 tokens (user input)\n  ↓\n  +700 tokens (Claude response)\n  ↓\n  Total: 2,400 tokens ← Previous turns STILL HERE\n\nExchange 3: User continues\n  ↓\n  +600 tokens (user input)\n  ↓\n  +900 tokens (Claude response)\n  ↓\n  Total: 3,900 tokens ← Conversation GROWS with each exchange"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Critical pattern"},{"type":"text","text":": Every message adds tokens. Every response adds tokens. Previous turns don't disappear. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The context grows with each exchange"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What Happens When You Hit the Limit?"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"At 200k Tokens (Standard Limit)"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Before 200k]\n  ✅ Claude remembers everything\n  ✅ Full conversation history available\n  ✅ Coherent long-form reasoning\n\n[Approaching 200k]\n  ⚠️ Older content starts being removed\n  ⚠️ Early parts of conversation may get forgotten\n  ⚠️ Compression begins\n\n[At/H over 200k]\n  ❌ Conversation stops working\n  ❌ Claude tells you it can't process more\n  ❌ You must start over or compact"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Specific behaviors:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Earlier parts might get compressed or forgotten"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Conversation stops working"},{"type":"text","text":" and you have to start over\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Older tokens are discarded"},{"type":"text","text":", retaining most recent"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude 4.5's Context Awareness"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"New capability"},{"type":"text","text":": Claude 4.5 models actually "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"know how much context window they have left"},{"type":"text","text":" in real time."}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Claude's internal awareness\nClaude knows:\n  - Total context capacity (200k or 1M tokens)\n  - Current token usage\n  - Remaining budget after each tool call\n  - When to pace itself on long tasks\n  - When to dig deeper vs. wrap up"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why this matters"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Plans accordingly"},{"type":"text","text":": Can navigate around limits instead of just hitting the wall\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Paces itself"},{"type":"text","text":": Adjusts output length based on remaining capacity\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tool call awareness"},{"type":"text","text":": Gets updated on remaining capacity after each tool call"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Most AI tools just hit the wall and stop. Claude 4.5 can navigate around it"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Context Window vs. Memory Features"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","cont